<p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">10</span>月<span style="font-family: Calibri;">12</span>日至<span style="font-family: Calibri;">13</span>日，校党委书记、督导专员江延湖，党委副书记、常务副校长李旺根一行<span style="font-family: Calibri;">6</span>人前往上海建桥学院、上海中侨职业技术大学等地调研交流期间考察、走访慰问了上海建业信息科技股份有限公司、上海德亚国际物流有限公司等在沪校友企业，开展访企拓岗活动。同时，还就筹备成立上海校友会等事宜与校友进行了交流</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></p><p style="margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-wrap: wrap; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 29pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-10-16%2011%3A27%3A04%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%207.png?Expires=2012786824&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Spg0ltEbp9coia8si4ntBmsGYjg%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-wrap: wrap; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 29pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-wrap: wrap; font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 29pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-10-16%2011%3A27%3A16%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%208.png?Expires=2012786836&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=KeBI6TMLR00YLEHVp%2BUvsINiaXU%3D" alt="" width="650" height="434" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p><br/></p>